{"id": 1629, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你其实会怎样衡量一个城市的“文明程度”？", "description": "总之不是快评选“全国文明城市”的时候街上环卫工人突然增多那种。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 4308, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170414154724Wo2mXunYcSgs5BFe.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-15T17:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 193280, "content": "在北京生活多年，去了上海被出租车卫生程度震惊到", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604214}, {"id": 193025, "content": "私家车少了，公交交通多了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993281}, {"id": 193281, "content": "行走路人脸上的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838530}, {"id": 193026, "content": "ofo折损率", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242458}, {"id": 193282, "content": "服务态度", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006876}, {"id": 193027, "content": "一些细节的人文关怀的设施", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 79433}, {"id": 193283, "content": "人们的生活态度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006879}, {"id": 193284, "content": "看出租车司机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003403}, {"id": 199173, "content": "汽车不鸣笛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958052}, {"id": 193029, "content": "对LGBTQ群体友善宽容 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006259}, {"id": 193285, "content": "公共设施", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985973}, {"id": 193030, "content": "路面、街面是否干净整洁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 102893}, {"id": 193286, "content": "街上没有垃圾，人们的言行举止", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982452}, {"id": 193031, "content": "听见汽车鸣笛的次数。安静的在后面等你慢慢通过 再找空间超越 在北京似乎很久没有听到那种对我有指向性的鸣笛 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700785}, {"id": 193287, "content": "自觉的人才是文明城市的标准。其他都是扯淡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950395}, {"id": 194311, "content": "敢不敢挤在人群中不把背包放到胸前", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009185}, {"id": 193288, "content": "这里写的每一条几乎都让我想到日本的城市。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590548}, {"id": 193033, "content": "不走紧急车道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006271}, {"id": 193545, "content": "iPhone 市场占有率", "image": "img/option/option/20170417183257nus8JCFjaBDVw7Ih.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924825}, {"id": 193034, "content": "公共厕所是否有卫生纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605600}, {"id": 193290, "content": "路人会不会热情回答你的问路", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006911}, {"id": 194570, "content": "人们脸上的幸福感和笑容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009896}, {"id": 193035, "content": "商场和景区厕所的干净程度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930069}, {"id": 193291, "content": "公共洗手间、火车站的文明程度", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767856}, {"id": 193037, "content": "旅游景点，还有没有乱涂乱画", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830690}, {"id": 193293, "content": "路边垃圾桶都是有用的，周围没有垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981800}, {"id": 193294, "content": "秩序程度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006926}, {"id": 193039, "content": "杭州的公交司机。行人才走到路边，就减速让行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977217}, {"id": 193040, "content": "大学校园里到处都是议论学术知识的声音", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963060}, {"id": 193296, "content": "城市角落的环境和公共厕所的密度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885578}, {"id": 193297, "content": "人文氛围更浓厚。独立书店增多 专业讲座增多 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948773}, {"id": 192786, "content": "大街上有没有口香糖，痰的印子。。。有没有烟头，餐巾纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 243, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991488}, {"id": 193043, "content": "poxi", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818967}, {"id": 193299, "content": "公共厕所的干净程度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 192788, "content": "大街上没有谩骂 坐车的时候没有争吵 和和气气的 都是高修养的样子 -", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001220}, {"id": 193044, "content": "不做作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925432}, {"id": 193556, "content": "公共卫生间的厕纸 马路上的烟头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007427}, {"id": 193045, "content": "不管你是什么，犯了错，得道歉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 373165}, {"id": 198678, "content": "坐公交车 排队 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018802}, {"id": 193814, "content": "地铁排队进去，出入口靠右站，哪怕是在商场也是这样～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771439}, {"id": 196631, "content": "穿着。虽然我不是对穿的不好的人有偏见，但是穿着打扮的确体现了城市文明程度。这里指的是整洁干净，不是花里胡哨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014942}, {"id": 193303, "content": "马路上垃圾桶和公厕的配比是否满足需求", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836414}, {"id": 193815, "content": "在意自己，也在意他人。平衡与适度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008038}, {"id": 192792, "content": "没有很多很多的电动车窜来窜去……", "image": null, "praise_count": 197, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627955}, {"id": 193048, "content": "街道干净，无小广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267950}, {"id": 193560, "content": "地铁公交，交通的情况。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818045}, {"id": 192793, "content": "杭州的司机", "image": null, "praise_count": 246, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914365}, {"id": 193049, "content": "医院和监狱的人数。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006314}, {"id": 193050, "content": "排队\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001856}, {"id": 193562, "content": "小黄车能不能骑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818045}]}